7kNvgHFlvyV&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYDRMRcdeoUAsRl5-JLJ2S5kBIlH3hrS4UgA3MANwHBgeA&oe=677925EE"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": null, "display_name": "Virtual Knockout", "keywords": ["Boxing", "VK", "Virtual", "Knockout", "Box"], "long_description": "### Virtual Knockout \n\nStep into the ring with **Virtual Knockout** the ultimate free VR multiplayer boxing game. Whether you're a beginner or a seasoned boxer, VK offers an immersive and exhilarating experience.\n\n**Features:**\n\n- **Multiplayer Mode**: \n  - **Public Lobbies**: Spar with players worldwide in exciting, competitive matches.\n  - **Private Lobbies**: Practice and compete with friends or selected opponents in a controlled environment.\n\n- **Training Arenas**:\n  - **Public Training**: Join sessions to learn new techniques and improve skills collectively.\n  - **Private Training**: Train solo or with a coach, focusing on specific areas like speed, power, or defense.\n\n- **Realistic Boxing Mechanics**:\n  - **True-to-Life Movements**: Experience authentic boxing with advanced motion tracking.\n  - **Dynamic Environments**: Fight in various arenas, each with a unique atmosphere and challenges.\n\n- **Customization and Progression**:\n  - **Avatar Customization**: Personalize your fighter with a wide range of options.\n  - **Skill Progression**: Track your progress, earn achievements, and climb the ranks.\n\nPrepare to enter the ring and prove your skills with Virtual Knockout!", "short_description": "Welcome to the first ever Free Quest Multiplayer Boxing Game! Join public or private lobbies and brawl!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/16nVx6NY4obMdecDeanQVyuQt7YWvr4kuDTn19ccpQ0U/edit?usp=sharing", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Phoze", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://docs.google.com/document/d/1YkGs89urCk65xODWdYlGF4bFnXxgmVktcYsBFWT1tn8/edit?